  "title": "Project Executive - Interior Fit Out",
  "description": "<p><strong>Successful candidate should possess the following:</strong></p>\n<p>Degree/Diploma/Certification in Architecture/Interior Design/Construction or Building Management or relevant studies with minimum 2 years experience in project management from budgeting, implementation to completion for retail and commercial projects.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Basic Roles and Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· To handle projects from inception to completion independently or with team/ immediate superior.</p>\n<p>· Be responsible for budget management, project schedule and execution of assigned projects.</p>\n<p>· Lead with ownership and manage clients, external and internal partners to ensure success delivery of projects.</p>\n<p>· To perform required SOPs including health and safety practices on site.</p>\n<p>· To ensure high quality and on time delivery on all project execution.</p>\n<p>· To manage inventory, materials and maintenance processes on assigned projects.</p>\n<p>· To handle and prepare all quality records and reports for assigned projects.</p>\n<p>· To be able to plan, initiate and manage work processes with efficiency.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Career Growth :</strong></p>\n<p>· To progress to lead and train a team to perform project works including A&amp;A and maintenance works.</p>\n<p>· To create excellent customer service and network with assigned clients and working partners both local and overseas.</p>\n<p>· To plan and manage project work independently including budgeting and middle management decision making.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The Person:</strong></p>\n<p>· Result-oriented and passionate to deliver projects successfully</p>\n<p>· Able to work independently with a high degree of integrity</p>\n<p>· Self-motivated with excellent interpersonal and communication skills</p>\n<p>· Good team player with value support and cultivate cooperation among colleagues</p>\n<p>· Meticulous and have eye for details.</p>\n<p>· Multi-tasking and able to meet tight datelines</p>\n<p>· Possessed driving license an advantage.</p>\n<p>· Proficient in MS Office applications.</p>\n<p>· Must be able to communicate in both English &amp; Mandarin.</p>\n<p>· Able to interact with all levels and a good team player.</p>\n<p>· Able to work within challenging and fast paced environment.</p>\n<p>. Must be able to travel.</p>",
